CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F310A1781527685
OL,3,CStarmer, world leaders and markets
OL,4,Cwelcome US-Iran deal
OL,6,FPrime Minister Keir Starmer joined
OL,7,FWestern leaders and global markets in
OL,8,Fwelcoming a peace agreement between
OL,9,Fthe US and Iran, which is set to see
OL,10,Fthe Strait of Hormuz reopened.
OL,12,FOn Sunday, Donald Trump and Iran
OL,13,Fconfirmed they had reached a deal, and
OL,14,Falthough the details of it have not
OL,15,Fbeen published the US president said
OL,16,Fon social media: "Ships of the World,
OL,17,Fstart your engines," referencing the
OL,18,Freopening of the strait.
OL,20,FHe added: "Let the oil flow!"
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/13
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,311,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31002
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F310A1781527685
OL,3,CStarmer, world leaders and markets
OL,4,Cwelcome US-Iran deal
OL,6,FThe announcement came shortly before
OL,7,Fthe US president departed Washington
OL,8,Fto head to a G7 meeting in France,
OL,9,Fwhere the Middle East will be high on
OL,10,Fthe agenda.
OL,12,FOther details in the agreement include
OL,13,Fthe end of the US naval blockade of
OL,14,FIran's ports and a framework for the
OL,15,Fremoval of Iran's nuclear capability.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/13
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,311,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31003
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F310A1781527685
OL,3,CStarmer, world leaders and markets
OL,4,Cwelcome US-Iran deal
OL,6,FPrime Minister Keir Starmer welcomed
OL,7,Fthe US-Iran peace deal. Speaking ahead
OL,8,Fof the G7 summit on Monday, the PM
OL,9,Fsaid it was a "hugely significant
OL,10,Fmoment," and congratulated Trump as
OL,11,Fwell as the mediators who helped get
OL,12,Fthe deal over the line.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/13
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,311,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31004
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F310A1781527685
OL,3,CStarmer, world leaders and markets
OL,4,Cwelcome US-Iran deal
OL,6,FHe said: "We have long called for de-
OL,7,Fescalation, and it is vital that all
OL,8,Fparties seize this opportunity to
OL,9,Fsecure stability in the region and
OL,10,Frestore freedom of navigation in the
OL,11,FStrait of Hormuz, which in turn will
OL,12,Fease the economic pressures felt by
OL,13,Fpeople here in the United Kingdom and
OL,14,Faround the world
OL,16,F"We will now work closely with our
OL,17,Fpartners to support this agreement and
OL,18,Fto ensure it turns into a durable,
OL,19,Flasting peace."
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/13
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,311,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31005
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F310A1781527685
OL,3,CStarmer, world leaders and markets
OL,4,Cwelcome US-Iran deal
OL,6,FForeign Secretary Yvette Cooper said
OL,7,Fthe UK stands "ready to help" develop
OL,8,Fthe US-Iran agreement into "a lasting
OL,9,Fpeace".
OL,11,FShe said: "I strongly welcome the
OL,12,Fannouncement of an agreement between
OL,13,Fthe US and Iran.
OL,15,F"It is vital that toll-free freedom of
OL,16,Fnavigation through the Strait of
OL,17,FHormuz is swiftly restored, so
OL,18,Finternational shipping can get moving
OL,19,Fagain to help the global economy and
OL,20,Ffamilies here at home.
OL,26,@oD@OOUoD@]O]pD@\OUqD@FO]sD@KOUwD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/13
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,311,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31006
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F310A1781527685
OL,3,CStarmer, world leaders and markets
OL,4,Cwelcome US-Iran deal
OL,6,F"The UK stands ready with France and
OL,7,Fother countries to support that
OL,8,Fprocess as needed."
OL,10,FAlthough Trump has said the Strait
OL,11,Fwill be reopened it will be months
OL,12,Fbefore traffic returns to normal.
OL,14,FBusinesses will want to see that the
OL,15,Fdeal lasts and that they won't get
OL,16,Fcaught up in a crossfire if the
OL,17,Fconflict suddenly restarted.
OL,26,@nD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/13
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,311,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31007
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F310A1781527685
OL,3,CStarmer, world leaders and markets
OL,4,Cwelcome US-Iran deal
OL,6,FThere are also major concerns about
OL,7,Fmines in the Strait, which the UK and
OL,8,FFrance have said they would be happy
OL,9,Fto take part in any demining operation.
OL,11,FStarmer also issued a joint statement
OL,12,Fwith the leaders of France, Germany
OL,13,Fand Italy.
OL,15,FThe joint statement from the so-called
OL,16,FE4 said aso "warmly" welcomed the
OL,17,Fagreement and thanked Pakistan, Qatar
OL,18,Fand all other mediators.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/13
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,311,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31008
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F310A1781527685
OL,3,CStarmer, world leaders and markets
OL,4,Cwelcome US-Iran deal
OL,6,F"This is a moment of opportunity to
OL,7,Frestore regional stability and
OL,8,Fstabilise the global economy."
OL,10,F"It is now vital that the detailed
OL,11,Fnegotiations are concluded and this
OL,12,Fagreement is implemented rapidly and
OL,13,Fcomprehensively. We are ready to
OL,14,Fsupport that effort."
OL,26,@rD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/13
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,311,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31009
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F310A1781527685
OL,3,CStarmer, world leaders and markets
OL,4,Cwelcome US-Iran deal
OL,6,FThey added: "The urgent re-opening of
OL,7,Fthe Strait of Hormuz with
OL,8,Funconditional and unrestricted freedom
OL,9,Fof navigation is essential. We are
OL,10,Fcommitted to playing our part to
OL,11,Fachieve this `in accordance with our
OL,12,Frespective constitutional
OL,13,Frequirements` including through a
OL,14,Fstrictly defensive and independent
OL,15,Fmission to reassure commercial
OL,16,Fshipping and conduct mine clearance
OL,17,Foperations.
OL,26,@nD@MOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G9/13
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,311,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31010
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F310A1781527685
OL,3,CStarmer, world leaders and markets
OL,4,Cwelcome US-Iran deal
OL,6,F"Iran must never acquire a nuclear
OL,7,Fweapon. We stand ready to work with
OL,8,Fthe US, Iran and the IAEA to this end.
OL,9,FWe are prepared to lift relevant
OL,10,Fsanctions in response to clear,
OL,11,Fverifiable steps by Iran on its
OL,12,Fnuclear programme.
OL,14,F"We will work intensively with the US,
OL,15,FIran and regional partners to seize
OL,16,Fthis moment, maintain momentum and
OL,17,Fachieve a long-term diplomatic
OL,18,Fsettlement.
OL,26,@nD@AOUvD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G10/13
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,311,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31011
SC,0011
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F310A1781527685
OL,3,CStarmer, world leaders and markets
OL,4,Cwelcome US-Iran deal
OL,6,F"We also reaffirm our full support to
OL,7,Fthe stability, sovereignty and
OL,8,Fterritorial integrity of Lebanon and
OL,9,Fthe importance of a robust ceasefire."
OL,11,FAs of Monday morning, Israeli Prime
OL,12,FMinister Benjamin Netanyahu had not
OL,13,Fcommented on the deal.
OL,15,FTrump criticised the Israeli leader
OL,16,Fheavily on Sunday for launching
OL,17,Fstrikes on Beirut, which risked
OL,18,Fderailing peace talks with Iran as the
OL,19,Fdeal was being finalised.
OL,26,@nD@AOUqD@fO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G11/13
