OL,3,CStarmer, world leaders and markets
OL,4,Cwelcome US-Iran deal
OL,6,FInternational markets have also
OL,7,Fwelcomed the deal.
OL,9,FSubscribe for free to our weekly
OL,10,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,11,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,12,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,14,FBenchmarks in Tokyo and Seoul
OL,15,Finitially gained more than 5% early
OL,16,FMonday. Oil prices fell more than #3 a
OL,17,Fbarrel.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G12/13
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
