FL,311,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31013
SC,0013
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F310A1781527685
OL,3,CStarmer, world leaders and markets
OL,4,Cwelcome US-Iran deal
OL,6,FThe future for the S&P 500 was up 1%
OL,7,Fand that for the Dow Jones Industrial
OL,8,FAverage gained 0.9%, indicating it
OL,9,Fwould be a good day in US markets when
OL,10,Fthey open.
OL,12,FStocks rallied in Asia, where Tokyo's
OL,13,FNikkei 225 gained 5.4% to 69,603.91 as
OL,14,Fthe benchmark logged another record
OL,15,Fhigh.
OL,17,FMarkets also rose in Australia, Hong
OL,18,FKong and South Korea.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G13/13
